Ready to create an online course and make sales in your sleep?! 💤

(📥 be sure to save this post)

Everyone and their mother wants to create passive income right now. And I’m here for it! 

But there are three simple things you need in place to be able to *actually* make sales in your sleep. 😴

…otherwise, you’ll likely waste a bunch of time and a lot of money trying to figure it out. 👎🏼 

1️⃣ Your audience must actually need your course. 🤯 I learned this one the hard way. When I first started out as a coach, I spent 100’s of hours and 1000’s of dollars creating my first online course. The problem was, I forgot to check to see if my audience actually needed it. 🤦🏼‍♀️ In other words, my first launch was a complete flop. Be sure to validate your offer *before* you create it. 😳

2️⃣ Your messaging needs to SLAP. 👋🏼 If your audience doesn’t know what the problem is that your course solves, they WILL NOT buy it. 🥲 Promote the solution your online course offers, not the product itself. 

3️⃣ Last but not least, you need an audience. But before you come at me, I’m NOT talking about your follower count or email list. 💥 I’m talking about using Instagram ads to get in front of your ideal clients who have a problem that your program solves. There’s a super simple way to do this and start making sales in less than one week. 

East peasy, right?! 😜 

Want my help setting this up??

Comment "SLEEP" below to get your hands on my proven formula to selling courses in your sleep (this is the same exact formula I’ve used to scale to $1M+ a year as an online coach for female entrepreneurs AND it’s the same formula 100’s of women inside my programs have been using with wild success too).

HOW I SCALED TO $100k+/MONTHS:

1. I created a low-ticket offer (online course) that solves a MAJOR problem for my audience. And instead of promoting the program itself, I focused on promoting the problem it solves.

2. I set up a funnel (Instagram ads) that do the heavy lifting for me. Instead of having to dance on Reels or show up on social 24/7 to sell my course, I focused my energy on getting my ads in front of the right people every day.

3. I made my course an “easy yes”. Instead of filling it with hours and hours of “filler” lessons, I focused on teaching nothing more and nothing less than what my audience needs to see fast results, using binge-worthy 5-7 minute lessons.

So yes, the course itself is less than $100 but it solves a problem my audience has in less than 2 hours. 🤯

Between the price point and my no BS, straight to the point lessons, this offer brings in sales on autopilot in my sleep.
